==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gobang
<hw>Go*bang"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>goban</asp>.]</altsp> <ety>[Jap. <ets>goban</ets> checkerboard, fr.
Chino-Jap. <ets>go</ets> checker + <ets>ban</ets> board.]</ety> <def>A
Japanese game, played on a checkerboard, in which the object of the game
is to be the first in placing five pieces, or men, in a row in any
direction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

